{"id":3069,"date":"2025-05-17T10:57:17","date_gmt":"2025-05-17T03:57:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=3069"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:34:43","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:34:43","slug":"dien-di-anh-sang-mun-viem","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/dien-di-anh-sang-mun-viem\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i\u1ec7n di &#038; \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec1m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i , t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n chu\u1ea9n Y Khoa s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 y t\u1ebf chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n ra ngo\u00e0i. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec7n di ion l\u1ea1nh gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2u trong da, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean da, gi\u00fap thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da sau n\u1eb7n, gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1i vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 &#8220;ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n&#8221; t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 60 \u0111\u1ebfn 90 ph\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 03 &#8211; 05 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -2px; top: 367px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3616,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[59],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-3069","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-advanced-skincare-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3069","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3069"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3616"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3069"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=3069"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?pos